# FS25 mod Lua — zip only (no relocations)

After editing any **`.lua`** under `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/src/`, **rebuild the install zip**. Do **not** copy or move icons or other assets from elsewhere in the project—only package what is **already** in the mod folder:

- `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/modDesc.xml`
- `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/icon.png`
- `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/src/` (entire tree)

## Command

From repo root (`MAIN CODEBASE`):

```powershell
powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\tools\Zip-FarmDashboardMod.ps1
```

This **replaces** `FS25_FarmDashboard_Mod/FS25_FarmDashboard.zip`. It reads the three paths above and writes the zip; it does not modify your source tree except creating/overwriting that zip.

## Agent behaviour

- After Lua changes in this mod, **run** that script from the project root (unless the user asks for source-only edits).
- **Do not** move or duplicate `icon.png` / `modDesc.xml` / `src` from other folders—only zip the existing mod directory contents.
